own: Shares owned prior to the transaction
control: Whether the acquirer gained control with the company
acq_ultimo: Acquirer market cap is based on a quarter before and after (ultimo)
tar_ultimo: Target market cap is based on a quarter before and after (ultimo)
cash_pct: Cash pct. used to pay for the target
fin_indu: True if target or acquirer industry is financial
acq_acq_oth: Acquirer as an acquirer: part of another deal during the period (1 if true)
tar_tar_oth: Target as an target: part of another deal during the period (1 if true)
tar_tar_oth_tom: Whether Thomson has registered other bids for the target
nsf_rd: Total R&D expenditures divided by net sales
assets_relprev: Relative assets compared to industry and pre merger asset level
